.Dt QLE 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm qle
.Nd QLogic ISP2400 Fibre Channel controller
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "qle* at pci?     " Pq PCI
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for QLogic Fibre Channel host bus adapters using
the ISP2400 family of chipsets.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr pci 4 ,
.Xr qla 4 ,
.Xr scsi 4
